This song is inspired by a simple melody that sounds familiar to everybody. I listen to this melody everyday at school, it's a notification which remind every student when the class begin or over. 
This song & melody remind me about beautiful moments we have at school. Thanks to God who gave those wonderful times. 
Just like school, there's first day of school, and there's graduation
Just like life, there's birth,and there's death
Just like those beautiful moments, there's start and there's end

This song "Notification" will remind you, if there is always a beginning, and there's always an end.

When you're sad, don't be too sad, because sadness will end soon, and happiness will begin to show up.
When you're happy, don't be too happy, happiness might be over anytime.

Always grateful :)
